<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Leave Approval Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
            padding-inline: 100px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
        }

        .leave-info {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .leave-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .approval-message {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .signature {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: right;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="main">
    <header>
        <h1>Leave Approval Letter</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="leave-info">
        <p>Dear <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>

        <p>We are pleased to inform you that your leave request for <%= numberOfDays %> days, starting from <%= startDate %> to <%= endDate %>, has been approved.</p>

        <p>Title of Leave: <%= leaveTitle %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="approval-message">
        <p>This decision is based on careful consideration of your request and the current workload. We appreciate your dedication to your work and hope you have a restful and rejuvenating leave.</p>

        <p>If you have any further questions or concerns, please feel free to contact the HR department.</p>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Your Company Name</p>
    </div>
    <div class="signature">
        <img src="/signature.png" alt="...signature">
        <p>your's faithfully</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
